<div class="m-invitation-mod clearfix">
    <div class="advertisement">
        <img src="/public/static/img/module/myInvitationBanner.jpg" alt=""/>
        <!--<a href="#/myInvitationRule" class="diff-btn" >活动规则</a>-->
    </div>
    <div class="u-normal-mod">
        <ul class="u-list">
            <% if(data.regCode && data.regCode.employeeNo){ %>
            <li>
                <a title="步步高员工">
                    步步高员工(<%= data.regCode.employeeNo %>)
                    <span class="g-fl-rg green">已认证</span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <% } %>
            <li>
                <a title="我的邀请码">
                    我的邀请码
                    <span class="g-fl-rg"><%= data.regCode.invitationCode %></span>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#/myInvitationList" title>
                    已成功邀请<%= data.regCode.invitedNum %>人
                        <span class="g-fl-rg orange">
                             查看详情 <span class="icon iconfont icon-youjiantou"></span>
                        </span>
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <% if(data.newUser){ %>
    <div class="u-normal-mod">
        <div class="u-title">
            <a title="助力邀请人">
                助力邀请人
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="u-cont">
            <div class="m-flex-box">
                <div class="input-box flex-box-item">
                    <input id="invitationCode" type="text" placeholder="请输入邀请人编码" pattern="[0-9]*"/>
                </div>
                <div class="btn-box flex-box-item">
                    <button id="invitationCodeSubmit" type="button"
                            class="u-btn u-radius u-btn-normal u-btn-block disabled">确定
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>
    <div class="u-normal-mod">
        <div class="u-title">
            <a title="好友邀请攻略">好友邀请攻略</a>
        </div>
        <div class="u-cont">
            <div class="qrcode-box clearfix">
                <div class="qcode">
                    <img src="/public/static/img/qcode.jpg" alt=""/>
                </div>
                <div class="qcode-text">
                    长按识别二维码，关注【小步之家】公 众账号，注册填写邀请码，就能助力您的好友哦！
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="summary-tip">
                <span class="iconfont icon-tishi"></span> 温馨提示：首次登录未提交邀请码，可在7天有效期内，进
                入【会员中心】-【我的邀请码】中填写哦！
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="qrcode-btn">
        <a id="invitationShare" class="u-btn u-radius u-btn-normal u-btn-block">呼朋唤友</a>
    </div>
